From karish Chuck Karish Subject Re Recommended bike for a tall In article John Tozer writes I am looking for advice on what bikes I should check I am ' tall and find my legs hips uncomfortably bent on most of the bikes I have ridden not many admittedly Are there any bikes out there built for a taller rider There's plenty of legroom on the Kawasaki A bit short in the braking department for spirited street riding but enough for dirt and for less agressive street Chuck Karish